{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01493ATzo9LiaKWVsDqgT7vJ","type":"tool_result","content":"     1→# AxenWP Fix Plan\n     2→\n     3→## Priority: HIGH\n     4→\n     5→### 1. [DONE] Add chat history cleanup to prevent unbounded table growth\n     6→- **Problem:** `chat_histories` table grows indefinitely — no TTL or cleanup mechanism\n     7→- **Impact:** DB storage bloat, slower queries over time, potential production outage\n     8→- **Fix:** Add a scheduled cleanup job that removes entries older than 30 days\n     9→- **Files:** `main.py`, `services/ai_service.py` or new cleanup utility\n    10→\n    11→### 2. [DONE] Async DB operations in chat history (sync blocking event loop)\n    12→- **Problem:** `PostgresChatMessageHistory.messages`, `add_user_message`, `add_ai_message` use sync `SessionLocal()` inside async `generate_response()`, blocking the event loop\n    13→- **Impact:** Increased latency on every AI response, reduced throughput under load\n    14→- **Fix:** Convert to async sessions or run sync operations in `asyncio.to_thread()`\n    15→\n    16→### 3. [DONE] Health endpoint should verify database connectivity\n    17→- **Problem:** `/health` only lists tenants, doesn't verify DB is reachable\n    18→- **Impact:** Health checks pass even when DB is down, misleading monitoring\n    19→- **Fix:** Add a simple `SELECT 1` check to the health endpoint\n    20→\n    21→## Priority: MEDIUM\n    22→\n    23→### 4. [DONE] Replace deprecated `datetime.utcnow()` calls\n    24→- **Problem:** `datetime.utcnow()` is deprecated in Python 3.12+ (used in models.py defaults)\n    25→- **Impact:** Deprecation warnings, eventual removal in future Python versions\n    26→- **Fix:** Replace with `datetime.now(timezone.utc)`\n    27→\n    28→### 5. [DONE] Remove unused `always_reply_with_audio` column\n    29→- **Problem:** Column exists in AIAgent model but is never read in application code (replaced by smart audio detection)\n    30→- **Impact:** Dead code / schema confusion\n    31→- **Fix:** Migration to drop column + remove from model\n    32→\n    33→### 6. [DONE] Add test infrastructure\n    34→- **Problem:** Zero test files in the project\n    35→- **Impact:** No regression safety net, risky deploys\n    36→- **Fix:** Add pytest setup + initial tests for core services (ai_service, token_manager)\n    37→\n    38→## Priority: LOW\n    39→\n    40→### 7. [DONE] Shared httpx client for GHL/Z-API services\n    41→- **Problem:** New `httpx.AsyncClient` created per-request in ghl_service and zapi_service\n    42→- **Impact:** Connection overhead, no HTTP/2 multiplexing or keep-alive benefits\n    43→- **Fix:** Use a module-level or app-level shared client with proper lifecycle\n    44→\n    45→### 8. [DONE] Debounce dict memory management\n    46→- **Problem:** `_ai_pending_tasks`, `_ai_message_buffers`, `_ai_debounce_config` dicts in zapi_receiver could accumulate stale entries if tasks fail unexpectedly\n    47→- **Impact:** Minor memory leak over long uptimes\n    48→- **Fix:** Add periodic cleanup or use WeakValueDictionary patterns\n    49→"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"c65344f3-6aa1-4b02-b3ae-01430f0d6aae","uuid":"1e7b8079-327a-4ab7-aae3-29548dd92854","timestamp":"2026-03-20T17:17:14.975Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/luizantonio/Documents/Antigravity/AxenWP/fix_plan.md","content":"# AxenWP Fix Plan\n\n## Priority: HIGH\n\n### 1. [DONE] Add chat history cleanup to prevent unbounded table growth\n- **Problem:** `chat_histories` table grows indefinitely — no TTL or cleanup mechanism\n- **Impact:** DB storage bloat, slower queries over time, potential production outage\n- **Fix:** Add a scheduled cleanup job that removes entries older than 30 days\n- **Files:** `main.py`, `services/ai_service.py` or new cleanup utility\n\n### 2. [DONE] Async DB operations in chat history (sync blocking event loop)\n- **Problem:** `PostgresChatMessageHistory.messages`, `add_user_message`, `add_ai_message` use sync `SessionLocal()` inside async `generate_response()`, blocking the event loop\n- **Impact:** Increased latency on every AI response, reduced throughput under load\n- **Fix:** Convert to async sessions or run sync operations in `asyncio.to_thread()`\n\n### 3. [DONE] Health endpoint should verify database connectivity\n- **Problem:** `/health` only lists tenants, doesn't verify DB is reachable\n- **Impact:** Health checks pass even when DB is down, misleading monitoring\n- **Fix:** Add a simple `SELECT 1` check to the health endpoint\n\n## Priority: MEDIUM\n\n### 4. [DONE] Replace deprecated `datetime.utcnow()` calls\n- **Problem:** `datetime.utcnow()` is deprecated in Python 3.12+ (used in models.py defaults)\n- **Impact:** Deprecation warnings, eventual removal in future Python versions\n- **Fix:** Replace with `datetime.now(timezone.utc)`\n\n### 5. [DONE] Remove unused `always_reply_with_audio` column\n- **Problem:** Column exists in AIAgent model but is never read in application code (replaced by smart audio detection)\n- **Impact:** Dead code / schema confusion\n- **Fix:** Migration to drop column + remove from model\n\n### 6. [DONE] Add test infrastructure\n- **Problem:** Zero test files in the project\n- **Impact:** No regression safety net, risky deploys\n- **Fix:** Add pytest setup + initial tests for core services (ai_service, token_manager)\n\n## Priority: LOW\n\n### 7. [DONE] Shared httpx client for GHL/Z-API services\n- **Problem:** New `httpx.AsyncClient` created per-request in ghl_service and zapi_service\n- **Impact:** Connection overhead, no HTTP/2 multiplexing or keep-alive benefits\n- **Fix:** Use a module-level or app-level shared client with proper lifecycle\n\n### 8. [DONE] Debounce dict memory management\n- **Problem:** `_ai_pending_tasks`, `_ai_message_buffers`, `_ai_debounce_config` dicts in zapi_receiver could accumulate stale entries if tasks fail unexpectedly\n- **Impact:** Minor memory leak over long uptimes\n- **Fix:** Add periodic cleanup or use WeakValueDictionary patterns\n","numLines":49,"startLine":1,"totalLines":49}}}
